text: Good Riddance Tour was the third concert tour by American singer-songwriter Gracie Abrams. It was to support of her first studio album, Good Riddance (2023). The tour began on March 6, 2023, in Chicago, United States, and ended on January 22, 2024, in Melbourne, Australia. ==References== Category:Gracie Abrams Category:Concert tours
